  DATA:
  FILE = dat_pa.dat;

  VARIABLE:
  NAMES   = id day N C sq m1-m20;
  CLUSTER = id;
  USEVAR  = N C s y1-y20;
  BETWEEN = N C;
  MISSING = .;
  LAGGED  = y20(1) s(1);

  DEFINE:
  CENTER N C (GRANDMEAN);
  s = sq / 10;
  y1 = m1 / 10;
  y2 = m2 / 10;
  y3 = m3 / 10;
  y4 = m4 / 10;
  y5 = m5 / 10;

  y16 = m16 / 10;
  y17 = m17 / 10;
  y18 = m18 / 10;
  y19 = m19 / 10;
  y20 = m20 / 10;

  ANALYSIS:
  TYPE = TWOLEVEL RANDOM;
  ESTIMATOR = BAYES;
  PROC = 8;
  FBITER = 50000;
  BSEED = 1213;

  MODEL:
  %WITHIN%
  resvar_1 | y1;
  resvar2-resvar19 | y2-y19;
  resvar_2 | y20;

  day_ar1 | y2 ON y1;
  day_ar2 | y3 ON y2;
  day_ar3 | y4 ON y3;
  day_ar4 | y5 ON y4;
  day_ar5 | y6 ON y5;
  day_ar6 | y7 ON y6;

  day_ar14 | y15 ON y14;
  day_ar15 | y16 ON y15;
  day_ar16 | y17 ON y16;
  day_ar17 | y18 ON y17;
  day_ar18 | y19 ON y18;
  day_ar19 | y20 ON y19;

  night_ar | y1 ON y20&1;
  beta_y | y1 ON s;
  delta_y | y20 ON s;
  beta_s | s ON y20&1;
  ar_s | s ON s&1;
  resvar_s | s;

  %BETWEEN%
  mu BY y1-y20@1;
  mu;
  [mu];
  [y1-y20@0];
  y1-y20@0;

  day_ar by day_ar1-day_ar19@1;
  day_ar*0.01;
  [day_ar*0.6](phi);
  [day_ar1-day_ar19@0];
  day_ar1-day_ar19@0;

  night_ar*0.01;
  [night_ar*0.15](alpha);

  resvar BY resvar2-resvar19@1;
  resvar;
  [resvar];
  resvar2-resvar19@0;
  [resvar2-resvar19@0];

  mu day_ar resvar_1 resvar resvar_2 night_ar-resvar_s s WITH
     mu day_ar resvar_1 resvar resvar_2 night_ar-resvar_s s;

  mu night_ar day_ar resvar_1 resvar resvar_2 ON N;
  beta_y delta_y beta_s ar_s s resvar_s ON N;
  mu night_ar day_ar resvar_1 resvar resvar_2 ON C;
  beta_y delta_y beta_s ar_s s resvar_s ON C;
  C;

  MODEL CONSTRAINT:
  NEW(diff_ar);
  diff_ar = phi - alpha;

  OUTPUT:
  TECH1 TECH8 STDYX FSCOMPARISON STAND(CLUSTER);

  PLOT:
  TYPE = PLOT3;
  FACTOR = ALL (500);

  SAVEDATA:
  FILE IS pa_sleep.dat;
  SAVE IS FSCORES (500);
